gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Hawks 116, Knicks 100
gameRecap.excerpt: The Hawks defeated the Knicks, 116-100. Jalen Johnson led Atlanta with 26 points, nine rebounds, and seven assists as De’Andre Hunter (22 points) and Dejounte Murray (21 points, nine rebounds, six assists) totaled 43 points. Donte DiVincenzo led six Knicks in double figures with 21 points as Bojan Bogdanovic added 19 points. Atlanta moves to 27-34 as the Knicks fall to 36-26.
